Package com.kneelawk.graphlib.api.graph.user.client

package com.kneelawk.graphlib.api.graph.user.client
This package contains interfaces that allow users to define custom client-side block-nodes for debug rendering.

Note that it is not required for every node to have a custom client-side version as well. The default client-side block-node implementation can cover most use-cases.
